<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-4728] KafkaConsumer#commitSync should clone its input </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-4728</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The `commitSync` method should clone input map to prevent live-lock in situation when user code uses synchronization on the map. Cloning the map prevents the consumer of the response to the `commitSync` request to block (this might be different thread than the original issuer of the request).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
